('COMMUNITY_BUILDING: L onboarding communautaire (presentation + premier post guide) reduit les lurkers de 30%.', 'Onboarding communaute = -30% lurkers', 'marketing', 'best_practice', 0.80, 'massive_boost_27', 'system'),
